  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Role: Infant Educator</strong></li><li><strong>AOP Childcare Centre</strong></li><li><strong>5 day | 7am - 7pm Rotate shift is a MUST</strong></li><li><strong>Entitled to  AWS + Performance Bonus </strong></li><li><strong>Work location:  Punggol / Bartley / Tampines </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Obtained at least a Certificate in Infant Care (CIT), Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY), Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), or its equivalent</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Role & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan and carry out the daily programme, developmental and care-giving tasks as assigned</p></li><li><p>Attend to the health, hygiene and safety needs of the infants</p></li><li><p>Create a safe environment and provide the best possible care to infants under their care</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain good rapport with parents<br /></p><p><br />#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p></p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p></p></li></ul>",
